    "description": "A structured mesh refinement study was conducted across three successive mesh densities (coarse: 1.2M cells, medium: 4.8M cells, fine: 19.2M cells) to establish grid-independent hemolysis index predictions. The Richardson extrapolation procedure was applied to quantify discretization error contributions at each operating point.",
    "activityType": "GridConvergenceStudy"
