      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal equivalency analysis demonstrating that validation experiment input parameters are representative of COU input parameter space; documented for all boundary conditions and material properties.",
      "rationale": "No formal equivalency analysis was performed between validation experiment inputs and COU inputs. Blood analog properties differ from patient blood at physiological hematocrit. Pump rotational speed range in validation does not fully span COU envelope. Flagged as epistemic gap."
