    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction has been formally reviewed. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated or flagged with documented epistemic gap justifications. The Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification satisfies the MRL 5 requirement for probabilistic characterization. The package is accepted for submission as a complete credibility evidence dossier, acknowledging that the decision on model adequacy remains Not Accepted pending resolution of the six unassessed factor gaps.",
